= blogs

Blog plugins for Redmine. Just like News :)

Original Author: KyAnh <xkyanh@gmail.com>
   http://www.redmine.org/boards/3/topics/5782

This code is based on above plugin.

Modified: Akiko Takano <akiko.pusu@gmail.com>

Customise points are following:
* Modify routing like this: /project/xxxx/blogs/action
* Move menu from application to project and we can host blogs per project and modify permissions.
* Separate tag cloud page from index.

